#: main.py:1211
msgid ""
"First time launch, please read: Once you have loaded a crossword, and wish "
"to load another one, you must first terminate the web app. IMPORTANT: If you"
" are on macOS, force quitting the application (using cmd+q) while the web "
"app is running will prevent it from properly terminating. If you mistakenly "
"do this, the program will run new web apps with a different port. "
"Alternatively, you can manually change the port in the program's config "
"file. All app processes that have not been properly terminated can be "
"terminated through Activity Monitor on MacOS, or, simply restart your "
"computer to terminate them."
msgstr ""
"Lansiad tro cyntaf, darllenwch: Unwaith y byddwch wedi llwytho croesair, ac "
"yn dymuno llwytho un arall, rhaid i chi derfynu'r app gwe yn gyntaf. PWYSIG:"
" Os ydych chi ar macOS, bydd gorfodi rhoi'r gorau i'r cais (gan ddefnyddio "
"cmd+q) tra bod yr ap gwe yn rhedeg yn ei atal rhag dod i ben yn iawn. Os "
"gwnewch hyn ar gam, bydd y rhaglen yn rhedeg apiau gwe newydd gyda "
"phorthladd gwahanol. Fel arall, gallwch chi newid y porthladd â llaw yn "
"ffeil ffurfweddu'r rhaglen. Gellir terfynu'r holl brosesau app nad ydynt "
"wedi'u terfynu'n iawn trwy Activity Monitor ar MacOS, neu, yn syml "
"ailgychwyn eich cyfrifiadur i'w terfynu."

